name: Frey AR
description:
For the past few years I have been creating Augmented Reality artworks with Eyejack, experimenting with my style and real world interactions. This is one of my earlier AR pieces first featured at Thoughtbubble Comic book festival in the UK as a life sized interactive cutout. It is now available as a limited edition NFT. 

Artist: Alexander Hare (Pixelpuncha). 
MP4: 960x960 pixels

High res prints and AR activations are available on request from Pixelpuncha.
